PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,FMedical experts are warning of the
OL,8,Fdangers of a trend for heating
OL,9,F"squishy" toys in the microwave after
OL,10,Fseveral children suffered serious
OL,11,Fburns.
OL,13,FVideos circulating online show the
OL,14,Ftoys, which are soft and easy to
OL,15,Fsqueeze, being heated to make them
OL,16,Feven softer.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,FHowever experts warn this causes
OL,8,Fpressure to build inside the squishy,
OL,9,Fincreasing the risk it may explode and
OL,10,Frelease the hot gel inside that can
OL,11,Fstick to the skin and cause severe
OL,12,Fburns.
OL,14,FThe Royal Hospital for Children (RHC)
OL,15,Fin Glasgow has treated six children
OL,16,Fwith injuries linked to the trend in
OL,17,Fthe past eight months, with some
OL,18,Fneeding surgery including skin grafts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,FOne of those injured was eight-year-
OL,8,Fold Joseph Erskine, from
OL,9,FClackmannanshire, who needed weeks of
OL,10,Ftreatment and a skin graft after a toy
OL,11,Fburst across his chest and hand in May.
OL,13,FHis mother Stephanie Ewing said: "My
OL,14,Fhusband and I were home. We were
OL,15,Fsitting in the living room next door
OL,16,Fwhen Joseph came in holding a towel to
OL,17,Fhis face.
OL,26,@uD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,F"He had already wiped off the burning
OL,8,Fgel which had also taken off his skin.
OL,9,FHe was saying that his squishy burnt
OL,10,Fhim and we initially thought he meant
OL,11,Fa chemical burn. Then he told us that
OL,12,Fhe had put it in the microwave.
OL,14,F"We were shocked as it had never
OL,15,Fcrossed our minds that he would do
OL,16,Fthat with a toy. He has never used the
OL,17,Fmicrowave before.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,F"One of us had heated something
OL,8,Fearlier and so the clock was already
OL,9,Fset at 40 seconds. Joseph just hit
OL,10,Fstart.
OL,12,F"It was that quick and easy for him."
OL,14,FShe said Joseph had seen the trend
OL,15,Fonline and she urged parents to chat
OL,16,Fabout it with their children and
OL,17,Fdiscourage them from doing something
OL,18,Fsimilar.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,FShe added: "Joseph's burn wouldn't
OL,8,Fheal on its own and required a graft,
OL,9,Fwhere skin was taken from his thigh
OL,10,Fand applied to his chest.
OL,12,F"He is normally such an active and
OL,13,Fsporty child with six clubs per week,
OL,14,Fbut all of that is on hold until he
OL,15,Fheals."
OL,17,FHer son must now avoid direct sunlight
OL,18,Fto the graft area for two years, which
OL,19,Fshe said will be "tricky over the
OL,20,Fsummer months".
OL,26,@oD@LOUtD@AOUwD@GO]{D@ROU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,FAnother young patient, 11-year-old
OL,8,FScarlet Rowe from Irvine in North
OL,9,FAyrshire, was treated for burns to her
OL,10,Fface and eyelid after a similar
OL,11,Fincident in May soon after she
OL,12,Freceived a squishy toy.
OL,14,FHer mother Gina said: "We didn't
OL,15,Frealise what had happened at first, it
OL,16,Fjust looked like slime on her face. It
OL,17,Fwas only after a few minutes we
OL,18,Frealised it had been heated and was
OL,19,Fburning her skin.
OL,26,@vD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,F"The swelling was so bad that we
OL,8,Fweren't sure what the outcome would be.
OL,10,F"Thankfully, no graft was required but
OL,11,Fit is so close to her eye that this
OL,12,Fcould have been a lot worse.
OL,14,F"These toys are very popular and easy
OL,15,Fto buy, but we had no idea about the
OL,16,Frisks. We had only bought them that
OL,17,Fday.
OL,19,F"I'd strongly advise parents to be
OL,20,Fvigilant and check what children are
OL,21,Fwatching and trying online."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,FBurns specialists said injuries caused
OL,8,Fby heated squishy toys can be
OL,9,Fparticularly severe because the gel
OL,10,Finside can remain extremely hot and
OL,11,Fget stuck to the skin, prolonging the
OL,12,Fburn.
OL,14,FSharon Ramsay, a burns nurse at the
OL,15,FRHC, said: "Unfortunately, we are
OL,16,Fseeing a growing number of children
OL,17,Fwith preventable injuries linked to
OL,18,Fthis trend.
OL,26,@wD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,F"When these toys are heated, the
OL,8,Fcontents can explode and stick to the
OL,9,Fskin, causing deep burns.
OL,11,F"These injuries can be very serious
OL,12,Fand may require long-term treatment,
OL,13,Fincluding surgery and rehabilitation.
OL,15,F"In some cases, children are left with
OL,16,Fpermanent scarring. We strongly urge
OL,17,Fparents and carers to speak to their
OL,18,Fchildren about the risks."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782704871
OL,3,CChildren burned by exploding 'squishy'
OL,4,Ctoys amid trend to heat them in
OL,5,Cmicrowave
OL,7,FHealing and recovery from burns can
OL,8,Ftake weeks or months and children who
OL,9,Fsuffer them often need ongoing care
OL,10,Fincluding dressings, physiotherapy and
OL,11,Fscar management.
OL,13,FThe Scottish National Burns Centre is
OL,14,Fhosted within NHS Greater Glasgow and
OL,15,FClyde.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
